column2: SELECT    p.ra AS sdss_p_ra, p.dec AS sdss_p_dec,    s.specObjId as sdss_s_specObjId, s.plate, s.fiberID, s.mjd, s.sciencePrimary, s.firstRelease, s.survey, s.instrument, s.programname,    s.ra as sdss_s_ra, s.dec as sdss_s_dec, s.z as sdss_s_z, s.zerr as sdss_s_zerr, s.zwarning as sdss_s_zwarning, s.class as sdss_s_class, s.subClass as sdss_s_subClass,    dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as sdss_p_type, p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z, w.cntr as sdss_w_cntr,    e.Flux_OIII_#, e.Flux_OIII_#_Err, e.Flux_Cont_OIII_#, e.Flux_Cont_OIII_#_Err, e.Flux_OIII_#, e.Flux_OIII_#_Err, e.Flux_Cont_OIII_#, e.Flux_Cont_OIII_#_Err,    e.Flux_Hb_#, e.Flux_Hb_#_Err, e.Flux_Cont_Hb_#, e.Flux_Cont_Hb_#_Err, e.Flux_NII_#, e.Flux_NII_#_Err, e.Flux_Cont_NII_#, e.Flux_Cont_NII_#_Err,    e.Flux_Ha_#, e.Flux_Ha_#_Err, e.Flux_Cont_Ha_#, e.Flux_Cont_Ha_#_Err,    g.oiii_#_flux, g.oiii_#_flux_err, g.oiii_#_cont, g.oiii_#_cont_err, g.oiii_#_flux, g.oiii_#_flux_err, g.oiii_#_cont, g.oiii_#_cont_err,    g.h_beta_flux, g.h_beta_flux_err, g.h_beta_cont, g.h_beta_cont_err, g.nii_#_flux, g.nii_#_flux_err, g.nii_#_cont, g.nii_#_cont_err,    g.h_alpha_flux, g.h_alpha_flux_err, g.h_alpha_cont, g.h_alpha_cont_err,    w.w1mpro, w.w1sigmpro, w.w2mpro, w.w2sigmpro, w.w3mpro, w.w3sigmpro, w.w4mpro, w.w4sigmpro, xm.match_dist as sdss_w_matchdist,    w.w1cc_map, w.w2cc_map, w.w3cc_map, w.w4cc_map, w.ph_qual_det1, w.ph_qual_det2, w.ph_qual_det3, w.ph_qual_det4 into mydb.MyTable FROM wise_xmatch as xm    JOIN SpecObjAll as s ON xm.sdss_objid = s.bestObjID    LEFT JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON p.objID = s.bestObjID    LEFT JOIN wise_allsky as w on xm.wise_cntr = w.cntr    LEFT JOIN emissionLinesPort as e on s.specObjID = e.specObjID    LEFT JOIN galSpecLine as g on s.specObjID = g.specObjID    WHERE (w.w1mpro-w.w2mpro)>=#    ORDER by sdss_p_ra
